name: Copter Duel
overview: Copter Duel is yet another two-player only vehicle vs. vehicle (in this case helicopters) shoot 'em up for the C64. As with all games of this nature, whoever has the most "kills" is the overall winner. You each have three helicopters each. This game was developed by Ronald Mayer and published by Tronic Verlag GmbH in Compute mit 1988/03.
